name: Stuyablo
body:
### Stuyablo

This game was created as a homework for AP Computer Science

```
$ git clone https://www.github.com/elc1798/stuyablo
$ cd stuyablo
$ sh compile.sh
```

If you want access to the test release (which will probably not even compile):

```
$ git checkout Release2.2-Unstable
```
